text: Asadul Haq Khasru is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Narsingdi-5. ==Career== Khasru was elected to parliament from Narsingdi-5 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Asadul Haq Khasru
